webstorm.desktop: a template for Linux

# Key bindings

Put file files to the configuration directory, the subdirectory `keymaps`:

- Mac: 'macOS copy.xml'
- Linux: 'GNOME copy.xml'

The paths to the configuration directory:

https://intellij-support.jetbrains.com/hc/en-us/articles/206544519-Directories-used-by-the-IDE-to-store-settings-caches-plugins-and-logs

- Mac: ~/Library/Application Support/JetBrains/<product>
- Linux: ~/.config/JetBrains/PyCharmCE2020.3 (and also in ~/.local/share)
